      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1034 - It was asked about a sick person who is unable to sit—whether they can pray while lying down and placing something on their forehead.\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, Allah (swt) has not burdened them beyond their capacity.\""
